milestones.description: Tendulkar and Rahul Dravid's 237-run partnership is IND's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 175 between Navjot Sidhu and Azharuddin
Tendulkar and Rahul Dravid's 237-run partnership is the highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 230 between Ijaz Ahmed and Saeed Anwar
This is the highest match aggregate (564) involving teams India & Kenya in ODIs
Aasif Karim has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (28) for KENYA, going past Hitesh Modi
